nodes.text: Underworld: A Galaxy of Scum and Villainy

Underworld: A Galaxy of Scum and Villainy is an article appearing in Star Wars Insider 89. It is written by Abel G. Peña and Ryan Kaufman, and illustrated by Joe Corroney. Its focus was on "bounty hunters, smugglers, mercenaries, crime lords and other assorted scum and villainy."
